precis:
Amendments to the IMPORT CONTROL LIST which place wheat, barley and their
products and certain dairy products on the List, for the purposes
of implementing the WTO Agreement on Agriculture by controlling their
importation, and ensuring that such products are permitted entry in
periods of scarcity in Canada.
